SUMMARY:Exit process form [@lcg]
DESCRIPTION:• ☐ HB start with email and share with Al\, Reika\, and Lisa G.
   TEAMS\n  with some restricted editing so students cannot modify.\n  • Ch
 atGPT 5.1\n• Lisa mentioned that she sends out slightly different emails\n
   depending on\, for example\, whether the student has already\n  defended
  or not.\n• Check other Graduate Program handbooks to see what they do.\n 
